main event: Civilians in Safi, Morocco reported seeing a luminous spherical object with what appeared to be jet engines in 1966.
interesting points: The object was seen by several trustworthy witnesses moving at a very high speed and low altitude.
The object was described as a red sphere with four jet engines that lit up the entire district as it passed overhead.
Witnesses confirmed the object had a spherical shape with four wings.
The object was observed heading towards the south.
The local meteorology station also confirmed the sighting of a luminous unidentified object passing overhead.
sighted object: a luminous spherical object with four jet engines
